    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.27a.5-7_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">5</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Albany Ore
                        April 16 - 59.
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear John:-</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Have been busy and have put off answering your letter which we all enjoyed.</p>
                
                <p>Im<sic>I'm</sic> sending you a package today. Do hope you will enjoy using it as much as I have enjoyed making it for you. Had it Started before I received your letter Hope the colors will be pleasing to you and do use it &#8212; and the price I ask is: a few
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.27a.5-7_0002"/>
                    
                <fw type="curatorial">6</fw>
                
                    <unclear reason="missing"/>ind thoughts <unclear/> If it brings you any comfort and happiness I'm satisfied.</p>
                    
                <p>Havent had much time to read in the books Mrs. Aly so kindly brought to me. They are very interesting.</p>
                
                <p>John has ask<sic>asked</sic> me several times to write you. He is quite well now. Was miserable for awhile with high blood pressure and very irregular heart action &#8212; he is better now only very lonly<sic>lonely</sic> Much better than a year ago. Hugh remains
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.27a.5-7_0003"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">7</fw>
                    
                    about the same. a very wonderful patient.</p>
                    
                <p>Have you heard how Mr. Aly is? Do hope he is fully recovered from his recent illness. They are both fine people.</p>
                
                <p>Hope your package arrives safely and do write when you can &#8212; we are looking forward to see<add>ing</add> you again this Summer.</p>
                
                <p><hi rend="underline">Absolutely no charges</hi> on the package. I did it because I like you and think you are a very wonderful person</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Edna John and Hugh Skillings</signed> <!--Possibly John Chaffee?-->
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
